This directory contains the ROLL program for
generating credits and annotations for $HOME MOVIES onlr roll is
built and installed by default

Contents:
 roll.1          roll program man page
 roll.c          roll program source
 croll.c         version of roll for color displays (not done yet)
 
 assemble.c      utility for pasting separate bitmap images together
 restore.c       generates a HOME MOVIE script out of a single image
 save.c          captures the screen as a MGR bitmap (same as getscreen)
 trim.c          crops bitmap images
 
 scripts/        sample roll scripts
 fonts/          fonts used by roll


